So for years I have been asked when I am putting on my own classic car show and here it is!





Ohsoretro Events are excited to present the OhSoRetro Show 2014, a celebration of all classic, vintage and retro cars
with special displays, show & shine awards, trade stalls, autojumble, live music, kids zone and much much more.

The OhSoRetro Show
Sunday 28th September 2014
10am till 4pm
St George's School, Westwood Road, Broadstairs, Kent, CT10 2LH

Public Entry - £5 per Adult, Under 16s free with accompanying adult
Classic Car Exhibitor - £7.50 per vehicle including driver and all occupants
Trade Stands - Starting from JUST £20

Due to limited space this event is prebook only, so please book early to avoid disappointment.
Car entry & Trade forms available on our website http://www.ohsoretro.co.uk

Public Entry tickets can also be purchased from our online store http://www.ohsoretro.co.uk

Split-Lee Collier
http://www.ohsoretro.co.uk
Info@ohsoretroevents.co.uk
075 44 33 82 82
